      <title>本周全球大宗商品市场值得关注的五大关键图表</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/five-key-charts-to-watch-in-global-commodity-markets-this-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新日铁公司对一家美国标志性钢铁制造商的重磅收购计划面临危险，拜登总统有理由在未来几天内取消这笔交易。美国主要枢纽的原油库存正在下降。严重的牛肉短缺正在损害美国牛肉行业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/five-key-charts-to-watch-in-global-commodity-markets-this-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
