      <title>特朗普助推的美元涨势明年年底将面临现实考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/dollar-s-trump-fueled-gains-face-a-reality-check-late-next-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的政策和美联储的降息可能会在 2025 年下半年给美元带来压力，华尔街开始对美元感到失望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/dollar-s-trump-fueled-gains-face-a-reality-check-late-next-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 17:25:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>24 小时降息结束全球央行宽松政策年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/fed-interest-rates-24-hours-of-cuts-that-end-year-of-global-easing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年是通货膨胀率下降到足以让大多数发达经济体开始放松货币政策的一年，而随着美联储牵头的 24 小时连续决策，这一年即将结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-14/fed-interest-rates-24-hours-of-cuts-that-end-year-of-global-easing</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Dec 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
